Features:
~~~~~~~~~
- support more dialects: Andrej's, Matlab, bc
- frontend should invoke compilers, etc. by itself
  - allow cpp-style preprocessing, #defines, etc.?
- add interpreter mode: iRRAM-bc, kirk-iRRAM
- add support for target backends: AERN2, Ariadne, iRRAM:TM, kirm
- support TGT's default math library functions in ccl's std libs
